----
<div class="titleblock">
==Tragic past, tragic future==
{{Quote|Understand that the tragic past is nothing short of a reward. It turns you strong emotionally and physically. However, a hidden past will only result in a sad future, and you can do nothing about it. You won't be the same, you'll develop depression, and you'll weaken until the future has nothing to reserve for you.|Gabriel Henderson ('''The Anatomy of Epiphanies''', 1994, chap. 2: "Tragic epiphanies", p. 17)}}
{{Quote|Fate is not something you can change from free will, but rather luck. Although one can try to save themself from such horrible fate, they will likely fail.|Gabriel Henderson ('''The Anatomy of Epiphanies''', 1994, chap. 2: "Tragic epiphanies", p. 18)}}</div>

<div class="titleblock"><span class="titlebox">Recovered Log</span>
<center>'''A post found in [[Backchat (Collaborative Log)|Back-Chat]] forums. Although now lost media, some information was recovered.'''<br></center>
'''Day 1:''' While we were exploring, me and the group separated after reaching [[Level 381|the Mindless Hills]], I'm not sure if they left, but I ended up in a familiar neighborhood. At first, I didn't think much of it- maybe it's a [[Level 9]] sublevel. But nothing here seems like [[Level 9|those suburbs]], it's so different... but so similar! I wish I knew what was happening, but I guess I'll find out as I go.

'''Day 4:''' Something weird that happened, I looked through a window and I saw myself? In [[Level 381|Mindless Hills]]? And I remember this, too, it happened like, last week! But this memory isn't quite accurate, I didn't make my way here, I made my way into... [[Level 118|the Cherry Blossom Park]]...? Huh?

'''Day 12:''' Y'know, now that I come to think about it, did the group lie to me? Did they just want to... get rid of me? They looked weirdly happy to be in [[Level 381|Mindless Hills]]... the tone of their voices sounded off, too. They weren't scared, or anything. I think I overheard them discussing that on the other room last month or so. Maybe they went to [[Level 118|Cherry Blossom Park]], and I didn't. What did I do wrong? Where did I go wrong? Why am I wrong? I don't know... I... just don't understand.<br>
</div>
<br>
