----
===Entrances===

*Entry is mostly random, traumatic events, or an epiphany may cause a wanderer to abruptly no-clip into here.
*No-clipping in the pitfalls of [[Level 994]] may lead here.
*Staying in therapy rooms for too long in [[Level 986]].
*Walking far enough in [[Level 897]]'s Funhouse.
*Getting stuck in certain cracks in [[Level 26.1]].
*Walking about in [[Level 381]].

===Exits===

* Jumping out of a window will likely lead to [[Level 993]].
*Walking about during the night or in the grasslands may take one to [[the Grand Medium]].
*No-clipping through anything with "Kaleidoscope" written on it is theorized to lead to [[Level 979]].
*Denying the epiphanies will lead to [[Level 18]].
*Walking around the streets may lead to [[Level 560]].
